<seg id="1"> Championship Hopeful but Not a Sure Thing </seg>
</hl>
<poster>
<seg id="2"> Loving Life and Luneng </seg>
</poster>
<seg id="3"> The gunpowder smoke of the Chinese Super Cup Soccer Game will soon bring flames of war. </seg>
<seg id="4"> The Luneng Team of Taishan is ready for the new game season, and is preparing to rush to the championship again. </seg>
<seg id="5"> The battles for seizing dominance among Lian, Lu, and Hu, the three strong teams, will break out at any moment. </seg>
<seg id="6"> Who will win the championship at last? </seg>
<seg id="7"> Based on an analysis of actual strengths, although the Taishan Team has a great hope of seizing the championship, it has no full certainty of success. </seg>
<seg id="8"> First, the time for new team members to adapt to each other is short. </seg>
<seg id="9"> The Taishan Team had nothing new last year. </seg>
<seg id="10"> The Taishan Team introduced Li Leilei and Wang Liang, the two members from the national team, this year. Soon after that, it will also add two members to the team from foreign teams, and its actual strength should be seen as increased, not reduced. </seg>
<seg id="11"> But because the national team is preparing for the matches with the Palestinian and Iraqi teams, those members of the national team cannot coordinate with the members of this team. </seg>
<seg id="12"> When they return to the football club, the league matches will start right away, </seg>
<seg id="13"> So, the issue of adapting to each other is the biggest issue the Taishan Team is facing. </seg>
<seg id="14"> I think that those members from the national team can be substitute players for the first several rounds of games in the league matches. </seg>
<seg id="15"> Firstly, they can be trained to adapt to the team in matches; </seg>
<seg id="16"> secondly, those national team members who have played two group matches can have a rest. </seg>
<seg id="17"> After several rounds of matches, their edge would be honed, and it won't be too late for them to participate. </seg>
<seg id="18"> Second, its defense has hidden problems. </seg>
<seg id="19"> The defense of the Taishan Team was scolded as a sick one by its fans last year. </seg>
<seg id="20"> Li Leilei was introduced this year, and has improved the defense, but the team has not reached the time for sitting back and relaxing. </seg>
<seg id="21"> The problem of center halfbacks' and fullbacks' slowness in turning back still exists, and those substitute players are either older in age or lack experience. </seg>
<seg id="22"> If center halfbacks and fullbacks can solidly play their roles, the Taishan Team would have one more advantage in its path to seizing the championship. </seg>
<seg id="23"> I think that it does not hurt to use Ren Yongshun who has good physical qualities, although lacking experience. He can exercise this year in preparation for the future. </seg>
<seg id="24"> And also, it is OK to withdraw Gao Rao to play fullback. </seg>
<seg id="25"> Many members of the Taishan Team can play fullback, including Cui Peng and Hai Bin. </seg>
<seg id="26"> Gao Rao is strong physically, and can aggressively and fiercely intercept the ball, and should be able to do a good job in the position of either center halfback or fullback. </seg>
<seg id="27"> Third, whether foreign players can adapt to the team. </seg>
<seg id="28"> The introduction of foreign players is a big issue that has been puzzling the Taishan Team. </seg>
<seg id="29"> Nobody dares to say anything good about Dan Qiu's performance last year. </seg>
<seg id="30"> It is known that foreign players have not been selected for introduction for this year. </seg>
<seg id="31"> I think that in addition to introduction of an outstanding forward, a very good left-foot forward should be introduced too. </seg>
<seg id="32"> Except Xing Rui, who played on the Taishan Team several years ago, there has not been a real left-foot player on the team. </seg>
<seg id="33"> Although some players like Cui Peng can play the role, a real left-foot forward would be much better than one who is a guest player. </seg>
<seg id="34"> If these three issues can be solved well, the path for the Taishan Team to seize the championship should be somewhat smoother. </seg>
<seg id="35"> As a Shandong football fan, I really hope that the Taishan Team will be able to seize the championship this year. </seg>
<seg id="36"> But frankly speaking, the Taishan Team is very hopeful, but has no full guarantee of winning the championship this year. </seg>
</DOC>
