<seg id="16"> So SME's in creative industries and similar services are unable to provide consultation to any significant extent. </seg>
<seg id="17"> Collecting high fees to advance one's own development in the end leads to a discouraging cycle. </seg>
<seg id="18"> Later, he came to Discuz. </seg>
<seg id="19"> Discuz is an outstanding forum program powered by PHP and MySQL. </seg>
<seg id="20"> With the help of Ramboo, a technical engineer from Beijing, Brandvista finally saw the light of day once again and hit the stage with matchless freshness. </seg>
<seg id="21"> The feedback was very good. </seg>
<seg id="22"> The interface was neat and friendly. </seg>
<seg id="23"> It was also very fast. </seg>
<seg id="24"> With the neat interface, writing a few words that moved me and inspired others, exchanging tidbits about work and life with friends from the same industry that shared the same pursuits, I began to find that this was a pleasure. </seg>
<seg id="25"> Thank you Discuz! </seg>
<seg id="26"> Recently, there has been a lot of news from the advertising industry. </seg>
<seg id="27"> Starting in January, the WTO system of openness in the ad industry began to be implemented. </seg>
